{"tid":2265339,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"2017年，我玩玩吓拍咗套Cyberpunk電影","createTime":"2020-10-31T10:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T17:39:57.000Z","uid":356371,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0eed14eaf2f979b56459844340d023e3154e0f","tid":2265339,"uid":356371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104684484743045/posts/129715442239949/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104684484743045%2Fposts%2F129715442239949%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak7idffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=37355ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104684484743045/posts/129715442239949/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然今日係萬聖節，但POST呢條片只係因為Cyberpunk展剛好完咗，呢條片本身係喺會場播，我想多啲人睇到就POST出嚟，當係俾大家嘅一份少少嘅萬聖節禮物吧（？）<br />\n當初拍呢條「香港大師」嘅時侯係2017年，當時好多事件都未發生，估唔到入面內容「警察有獨立部隊濫用私刑」「私刑部隊嘅龍頭大哥原來係古惑仔同大財團勾結」「有人同時操控黑白兩道食兩家茶禮」；當時拍「香港大師」，唔多唔少都係因為玩鬧同過癮玩膠而拍，估唔到而家睇返，多咗一種苦澀嘅感覺。<br />\n2020年，其實細個覺得係遙不可及嘅未來，原來一轉眼已經到咗，而我哋同好多Cyberpunk作品所形容嘅黑暗未來，其實真係冇乜大分別。<br />\nCyberpunk對我嚟講嘅意義，係「呈現人類可見的黑暗未來 防止人類踏上相同道路」，希望我哋由80年代睇咗咁多呢類電影，除左識玩紅藍撞色，加啲中文字玩Neon light之外，都學得到裡面嘅少少教訓。<br />\n<br />\n-梁仲文<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnD3j4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnnD3j4g.jpg&h=0b36b5c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmgXpvX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmgXpvX.jpg&h=55913d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvH0nhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvH0nhD.jpg&h=085e507c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfKxXQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfKxXQZ.jpg&h=00887c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMNcdpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMNcdpk.jpg&h=14d4c6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrCjCQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrCjCQ0.jpg&h=c8f2a7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dE8KOXJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdE8KOXJ.jpg&h=99472965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港大師 HongKongMaster (Movie)<br />\n導演 梁仲文<br />\n編劇 李頌仁（恐懼鳥）<br />\n主演 張進翹 譚淇淇"},{"pid":"d49855ddc29680e3514caf6ee8cfcf01acb7fedf","tid":2265339,"uid":27996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"當年有去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb9c075e1a615c51637b7906f7d70fc096a932d","tid":2265339,"uid":356371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d49855ddc29680e3514caf6ee8cfcf01acb7fedf","tid":2265339,"uid":27996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"當年有去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然上咗好少場冇乜人睇過 不過呢幾場 場場都爆其實好感動"},{"pid":"5e1f070242d59df2244260f04eed853e43ac4db4","tid":2265339,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"譚淇淇好趕客<br />\nBut G持你"},{"pid":"45630d9bdda0c921ff9bf469eaeb62409ee3d148","tid":2265339,"uid":356371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1f070242d59df2244260f04eed853e43ac4db4","tid":2265339,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"譚淇淇好趕客<br />\nBut G持你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7c3b8826ebdf9026fac36bbe51609a59f1994f","tid":2265339,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45630d9bdda0c921ff9bf469eaeb62409ee3d148","tid":2265339,"uid":356371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1f07